data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Boardman schools that sits in a private back cul-de-sac. Make your way in from the sprawling covered front porch and be greeted w/ a grand 2 story foyer. A 1st floor office is off of the foyer. Down the hall leads to the dining room connected to the the large eat-in kitchen that has an abundance of cabinets and granite countertop space and a nice sized island. Open to the kitchen is a very good sized family room w/ gas fireplace. A 1st floor laundry & updated half bath completes the main floor. The kitchen and family room looks out the back to your stamped concrete patio w/ built in firepit. The back view looks over an abundance of undeveloped land. The second floor has a spacious master suite along with the other 3 good sized bedrooms. The basement has recently been drywalled w/ brand new flooring and is plumbed for another full bathroom. The 2.5 heated garage includes custom cabinets, stainless sink, and additional single garage door off the back. Dormers were added to this home to give it a stately look about 4 years ago along with a new roof. So much has been done to this home so come Schedule your showing to see for yourself!
